			<h3>The Project</h3>
			<p>The Codealia project is an initiative of the UK-based non-profit organization Agile Ventures.  Agile Ventures develops IT solutions for customers in the non-profit sector. </p>
			
			<p>We are dedicated to crowdsourced learning and Agile software development using pair programming technologies, code reviews and daily scrums.</p>

			<p>Find our website at <a href="http://www.agileventures.org">www.agileventures.org</a> or check out our <a href="http://www.facebook.com/AgileVentures">Facebook page</a>.</p>
		</div> 
